                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        <!-- /.container -->

    </div>
    <!-- /.content-section-a -->

    <div class="content-section-b">

        <div class="container">

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-offset-1 col-sm-push-6  col-sm-6">
                    <hr class="section-heading-spacer">
                    <div class="clearfix"></div>
                    <h2 class="section-heading">Don't let sky high credit card fees ruin your bottom line!</h2>
                    <p class="lead">FBOs loose 4% and higher of profit in Credit Card fees.  Luckily, aircraft operators are choosing AirportAccount.com as a smarter way to pay.  They benefit from a simple single platform to manage thier expenses - You benefit from lower rates and more finanical security! </p>
